title: [FSX] FSDreamteam GSX Ground Services X
description:
FSDreamteam GSX for FSX 

download the demo from here : http://www.fsdreamteam.com/fsdreamteam/products_gsx.html

1.install the demo
2.run the .reg file 
3.start your fsx , press alt in the addon section find addon manager , click on it , go to FSDreamteam , click on GSX , then use this key and register GSX manually : 

'' FSDTGSX-4X4J-BCTY-YHPV-RTE9-1A31 ''

Enjoy :)

Req : FSDreamteam US airports , Flightbeam KIAD washington
